@model Blog
@section FullWidthImage {
    <img src="@Url.Content(Model.BlogImage)" alt="" class="w-full h-80 object-cover object-top">
}

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 mt-12">
    <!-- Başlık -->
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">@Model.Title</h1>
    <p>@Model.User?.FullName</p>
    <p>@Model.CreatedDate</p>
    <!-- Giriş -->
    <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6">
        Risk management is a crucial aspect of personal, organizational, and financial decision-making. It involves
        identifying, assessing, and controlling potential risks that could hinder the achievement of objectives. From
        financial institutions to tech startups, risk management is a core function that ensures stability and growth in
        uncertain environments.
    </p>

    <!-- Alt Başlık -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">What Is Risk Management?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Risk management is the process of anticipating, analyzing, and mitigating risks to reduce their impact. It
        includes both proactive and reactive strategies to minimize threats and maximize opportunities. While the term
        "risk" often carries a negative connotation, it is also about leveraging calculated risks for potential gains.
    </p>

    <!-- Anahtar Elemanlar -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Key Elements of Risk Management</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-3">
        <li><strong>Risk Identification:</strong> The first step is identifying all potential risks (financial,
            operational, strategic, and compliance risks).</li>
        <li><strong>Risk Assessment:</strong> Analyze each risk based on likelihood and impact to prioritize actions.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Risk Mitigation:</strong> Implement actions to reduce the probability or impact of risks.</li>
        <li><strong>Monitoring and Review:</strong> Regularly evaluate risks and adjust strategies as needed.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Önemi -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Why Is Risk Management Important?</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-3">
        <li><strong>Protecting Assets:</strong> Safeguard both tangible and intangible assets, like intellectual
            property and reputation.</li>
        <li><strong>Enhancing Decision-Making:</strong> Balance potential benefits and threats for better decisions.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Regulatory Compliance:</strong> Avoid fines or penalties by meeting industry regulations.</li>
        <li><strong>Building Resilience:</strong> Prepare for uncertainties, minimizing disruptions and ensuring faster
            recovery.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Araçlar -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Tools and Techniques in Risk Management</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-3">
        <li><strong>SWOT Analysis:</strong> Identify Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, and Threats.</li>
        <li><strong>Risk Matrices:</strong> Plot risks based on likelihood and impact to prioritize effectively.</li>
        <li><strong>Scenario Analysis:</strong> Simulate scenarios to evaluate risk outcomes.</li>
        <li><strong>Risk Management Software:</strong> Tools like RiskWatch and SAP Risk Management automate complex
            tasks.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Örnekler -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Examples of Risk Management in Action</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Risk management is applied across various industries:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-3">
        <li><strong>Financial Sector:</strong> Banks use stress testing and portfolio diversification.</li>
        <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Hospitals prepare for pandemics with resource stockpiles.</li>
        <li><strong>Tech Industry:</strong> Companies invest in cybersecurity to protect user data.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Sonuç -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        Risk management is not about avoiding risks altogether but understanding and preparing for them. Whether
        managing personal finances, running a business, or navigating daily life, effective risk management helps reduce
        vulnerabilities and seize opportunities. By adopting a structured approach, risks can become catalysts for
        innovation and growth.
    </p>
</div>